      <p align="justify"><a name="ad_management"><b><font color="#FF0000">ADVERTISING 
        MANAGEMENT</font></b></a><br>
        This area allows the Administrator to create different views based on 
        such factors as Company, Location and Status. From this screen, the Administrator 
        will be taken to the Client Profile screen where the Administrator can 
        administer the Advertisers' Accounts. 
      <p> 
      <p align="justify"><a name="expiration_meter"><b><font color="#FF0000">TOOL: 
        EXPIRATION METER</font></b></a><br>
        This function allows the administrator to view ads by expiration parameters 
        (such as expire by impressions, clicks or date) and timeframe (such as 
        Last Month, This Month or Next Month). 
      <p> 
      <p align="justify"><a name="avg_click_by_location"><b><font color="#FF0000">TOOL: 
        STATISTICS OF AVERAGE CLICK THRU BY LOCATION</font></b></a><br>
        This function allows the administrator to view the average <i><b>CLICK</b></i> 
        of the advertisements grouped <b><i>LOCATION</i></b>.<br>
      <p> 
      <p align="justify"><a name="avg_imp_by_location"><b><font color="#FF0000">TOOL: 
        STATISTICS OF AVERAGE IMPRESSION BY LOCATION</font></b></a><br>
      This function allows the administrator to view the average <i><b>IMPRESSION</b></i> 
      of the advertisements grouped <b><i>LOCATION</i></b> and the period of time 
      entered.<br>
